msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Widget ine simba, yemahara yekuvhura uye kubhadhara inobvumira vashanyi vako"
" kukutsigira kuburikidza neKadhi reKredhiti kana cryptocurrency (Quai). "
"Hapana mari yemwedzi, hapana mhando dze subscriptions dze third-party – "
"chete wallet yako uye mabasa emahara."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Mamwe ma browser anobvisa third-party scripts kuti ave chengetedzo. Proxy "
"iyi inodhiraivha script kuburikidza ne server yako kuti ibvise block aya."

